{
  "stem": "26140.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But later on, in about half a year later, they employed the women from Birkneau to work on the farm, and we were employed as a subsidiary force for the supply of various items to the Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Auschwitz, it was very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- every time you had to look over your shoulder that nobody will beat you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The worst-- the worst thing was lack of food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would have survived the beating, but the lack of food made it worse.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The German stated that, on this food, you will survive three months unless you get somewhere else food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People who survived were mainly those who tried to manage to steal some food in order to survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Usually when the kommandos were out for work, they tried to look where they can pinch something, either a potato or beet or carrot and-- and eat it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or, usually, when the kommandos came back from work, there used to be many people who couldn't survive the day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the block managers did not report their death to the kitchen officials in the first few days, so that they can collect their food.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if you have friends there, they can always give you a helping hand in food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was very good at certain times, but later on, I felt very ill.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had scratched my foot on a-- on a very hard shoe, and this turned down into phlegmon, which means in-- I had to go to hospital for treatment.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I managed to get an operation done on my leg, in order to remove all the bad blood.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that, I survived and came back to the block.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My weight was very, very much down.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
